import { Card,Button } from "react-bootstrap"
function Courseitem({img,title,text}){
    return(
        <Card >
        <Card.Img variant="top" src={img} />
        <Card.Body>
          <Card.Title> {title} </Card.Title>
          <Card.Text>
           آ
          </Card.Text>
          <Button variant="primary">خرید دوره</Button>
        </Card.Body>
      </Card>
    )
}
export default Courseitem
